<div class="page-header">
  <h2>Import Image</h2>
</div>

<div class="no-external-nic-alert alert alert-warning" style="display:none">
    <h5><strong>Warning: No External Network Interface</strong></h5>
    Image API does not have an external network interface. In order to import images from an external repository, you must first attach an external NIC to Image API.<br/><br>
    <a href="" class="imgapi-vm-btn btn btn-info btn-sm">Process to Image API VM to add an external NIC</a>
</div>

<div class="source-select row">
    <form>
    <div class="col-sm-3" style="padding:0; padding-left: 15px;">
        <select class="form-control image-source">
            <option value="https://images.smartos.org/">images.smartos.org</option>
            <option value="https://updates.tritondatacenter.com/">updates.tritondatacenter.com</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-7" style="padding:0;">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Search by image name or exact UUID" class="form-control"/>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-2" style="padding:0; padding-right: 15px;">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-block btn-primary btn-info search"><i class="fa fa-search"></i> Search</button>
    </div>
</form>
</div>


<h3>Select Image to Import</h3>
<div class="images-list-region"></div>
<button class="btn btn-block btn-info load-more">Load More</button>
